               <text>
                  <paragraph>SELECT-OB<sup>®</sup> is available as a light blue caplet debossed EV0077. Available in bottle of 90, (NDC 0642-0077-90).</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20140922"/>
               <component>
