                     <id root="2c809964-17d0-47e8-a5ed-8d90c370f0a0"/>
                     <code code="44425-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="STORAGE AND HANDLING SECTION"/>
                     <text>
                        <paragraph>Store at room temperature, approximately 15°-30°C (59°-86°F), avoid excessive heat and moisture.</paragraph>
